    "We show that injected-thought detection-one component of introspective behavior-can be directly induced through fine-tuning, rather than waiting for emergence.2.",
    "Transient Injection Paradigm.",
    "We demonstrate detection of single-token injections-a more temporally localized task than the persistent injection used by Lindsey [2025] for this task.3.",
